snippet.title: ENG vs WI | 3rd T20I | Cricket Highlights | West Indies Tour Of England | 10th June 2025
snippet.description:
England secured a dominant 37-run victory over West Indies in the 3rd T20I at Utilita Bowl, Southampton. Batting first, England posted a massive 248/3 in 20 overs, with Ben Duckett leading the charge with an explosive 84 off 46 balls. West Indies fought hard but fell short, managing 211/8 in their chase. With this win, England completed a 3-0 series sweep, asserting their dominance in the shortest format.

This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Superman | Tickets on Sale Now
snippet.description:
On July 11, the entire world will look up. Get tickets now for #Superman - Only In Theaters and @IMAX 

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù) and editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, ‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Ghatak :-
Kashi Nath is a kind-hearted wrestler and the dutiful adopted son of Shambhu Nath, living in Banaras. Shambhu Nath, who was a freedom fighter awarded with the Tambra Patra, is an honourable and respectable man in town. Kashi, along with Shambhu, comes to Mumbai for medical treatment for Shambhu and stays with his brother, Shiv Nath. Kashi meets Gauri in the colony and starts liking her. He learns that the colony is being terrorized by the tyrannical gangster, Katya, along with his six brothers. Before Kashi's arrival, a resident named Sachdev tried to initiate a revolt against Katya, but got ruthlessly killed by him, thereby making Malti, Sachdev's wife, go mad. Katya and his brothers become enemies with Kashi when he beats up their goons in the process of roughing up Malti.

Ghatak :-
Kashi Nath is a kind-hearted wrestler and the dutiful adopted son of Shambhu Nath, living in Banaras. Shambhu Nath, who was a freedom fighter awarded with the Tambra Patra, is an honourable and respectable man in town. Kashi, along with Shambhu, comes to Mumbai for medical treatment for Shambhu and stays with his brother, Shiv Nath. Kashi meets Gauri in the colony and starts liking her. He learns that the colony is being terrorized by the tyrannical gangster, Katya, along with his six brothers. Before Kashi's arrival, a resident named Sachdev tried to initiate a revolt against Katya, but got ruthlessly killed by him, thereby making Malti, Sachdev's wife, go mad. Katya and his brothers become enemies with Kashi when he beats up their goons in the process of roughing up Malti.

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

snippet.title: Middle Class Ki Soch Ko Badalna Seekho | By Sandeep Maheshwari
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

Witness the heartwarming story of brotherhood and family values in "Om Jai Jagadish." Released in 2002, this Hindi film beautifully portrays the lives of three brothers and their unwavering bond despite facing various trials and tribulations. When their father passes away, the eldest brother, Om, selflessly takes on the responsibility of caring for his younger siblings, Jai and Jagadish. As they navigate life's challenges, including financial difficulties and personal aspirations, their unity is tested. Will their strong familial love withstand the pressures of the outside world? Experience a captivating narrative filled with emotion, drama, and memorable performances from a stellar cast.

In Weekend Ka Mahabharat, the battlefield isn't Kurukshetra ‚Äî it's the living room! üè†‚öîÔ∏è
Prashant and Sayali, your favorite desi couple, go head-to-head in the ultimate weekend showdown. Prashant dreams of a peaceful weekend with snacks and sleep, while Sayali is all set with plans to go out, explore, and make "memories." What starts as a casual discussion quickly turns into a hilarious war of logic, drama, and emotional blackmail! üòÖ‚ù§Ô∏è

snippet.title: Finding Best Paschim Vihar Food With AI Purav Jha In Delhi | Tere Gully Mein Ep 107 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

In this fun-filled episode of Tere Gully Mein, we meet India's Top Youtuber & the one who cracks us up with hilarious mimicry and crazy characters, it's none other than the OG Youtuber @Puravjha_  

This time we go out on the streets of Delhi's Paschim Vihar and explore some iconic hotspots there. Purav is a total foodie and this episode clearly proves that!  

From Little Chef's juicy rolls and wraps to his all-time comfort ice cream spot, Gianis and the ever-crowded Sandos restaurant which is popular among the locals for its north indian delicacies, this episode is your all-access food guide whenever you're in West Delhi. 

What else? Well, we also play a few fun games to bring out the real, candid side of Purav that included Never Have I Ever, a crazy Mimic challenge and ultimately the one where he gets to describe the fellow youtubers and content creators in one word each. It gets way too real! (Something you wouldn't want to miss!)

From talking about his first career break with Harsh Beniwal. his equation with him today to his lady love and his Bihari dialect, he talks about it very candidly. Purav also talks about his skincare routine (because of his girlfriend :D), his most expensive purchase till date and also shares his feelings on getting trolled.

Watch Purav Jha like never before! This video will make you fall in love with him again and will also make you admire his talent even more.

snippet.title: Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Motion Rao | Father & Son Comedy Blast | MCM Special Episode
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu  Motion Rao | Father & Son Comedy Blast | MCM Special Episode
When Madhu‚Äôs small mistake turns into his father's big ‚Äúmotion‚Äù disaster, the entire village gets involved in this hilarious chaos! üíäüòÇ

Dr Satish Kumar is a widely respected Pastor, Author, International speaker and Humanitarian.
 His powerful preaching, visionary leadership and Integrity have earned him much respect and following not only in India but around the world.

He is known for his emphasis on strong moral values, compassion and commitment to biblical standard of living. Despite his vast following and influence, Dr Satish Kumar remains a humble Man of God, who loves people and is accessible to all.

His commitment to integrity, transparency, and authenticity in ministry and life has earned him much respect both in India and around the world.

His extraordinary vision, leadership capabilities and unwavering faith have resulted in him building the biggest Church in Asia with more than 400,000 members.

Dr Satish Kumar is also a globally recognized figure featuring widely on various international platforms.

He has been conferred the Doctor of Divinity degree from ‚ÄòThe Dallas Baptist University‚Äô and the ‚ÄòMother Teresa‚Äô award for his service to humanity. He is also the Honorary Board Member of ‚ÄòMuseum of the Bible‚Äô Washington and also a Board member of CGI International, founded by Dr. Paul Yongi Cho, of South Korea.

He has been widely recognized for his humanitarian work, particularly during the COVID-19 pandemic, where he organized hundreds of volunteers to deliver food kits to the needy and suffering. He has also been instrumental in various community service projects, such as free medical clinics, food distribution programs and retirement homes.

He is a much sought after international speaker, who passionately communicates God‚Äôs Word. His messages air on 300 different television programs each month in several Indian languages, reaching millions in India and around the world.

Calvary Temple Hyderabad was built in just 52 days, which is a remarkable achievement. It is now the biggest church in Asia with more than 400,000 members. The dynamic worship, diverse congregation, biblical teachings and supportive environment make it an amazing place to worship and fellowship. Calvary Bible college, Calvary hospital, and Calvary school are offshoots of Calvary Temple and provide much needed education and health care to all its members. Calvary Temple is beautifully built and is one of the major attractions in Hyderabad featuring in the ‚ÄòTop places to visit‚Äô on Trip advisor and other travel portals. Hundreds of people visit Calvary Temple every day to enjoy the serenity and the admire the beautiful edifice. You are invited to visit and worship at Calvary Temple Hyderabad and experience Gods presence and listen to His Word.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
